  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is conducted Asia, Europe and North America. The aim of this study is to describe
      insulin therapy adherence and the burden of non-adherence on patient functioning, well-being
      and diabetes management.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
